    <title>Tmux</title>
    <link href="/2022/08/14/Tmux/"/>
    <url>/2022/08/14/Tmux/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安装：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs linux"><br># Ubuntu 或 Debian<br>sudo apt-get install tmux<br><br># CentOS 或 Fedora<br>sudo yum install tmux<br><br># Mac<br>brew install tmux<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs linux">tmux new -s &lt;session-name&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>分离会话：<br>先按下<code>Ctrl+b</code>再按下<code>d</code></p><p>输入以下代码查看tmux窗口列表：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs linux">tmux ls<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接入会话：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs linux">tmux attach -t &lt;session-name&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>杀死会话:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs linux">tmux kill-session -t &lt;session-name&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>切换会话：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs linux">tmux switch -t &lt;session-name&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重命名会话：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs linux">tmux rename-session -t &lt;session-name&gt; &lt;new-name&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>快捷键：</p><ul><li>Ctrl+b d：分离当前会话。</li><li>Ctrl+b s：列出所有会话。</li><li>Ctrl+b $：重命名当前会话。</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
